{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_02_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫 1話 SNSの声",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロが東京に移転してしばらく経ち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A while after Hoshimi Productions moved to Tokyo",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のライブも盛り上がったし……\nまずは順調な滑り出し――ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesterday’s show was really lively‚\nand things are getting off to a smooth start… Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、どうした？　雫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning. What’s wrong‚ Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございま……ふぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good mor… *sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい、挨拶が途中でため息になってるじゃないか\nどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ your greeting changed to a sigh in the middle.\nWhat’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "これを……見てた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was looking at this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "SNSを早速チェックか。雫らしいな\n昨日のライブのこと、もう書き込みがあるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re already checking on social media. Typical Shizuku.\nThere are already comments about yesterday’s show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "私のせいで、イマイチだったって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say it was my fault that it wasn’t good enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　昨日は歌もダンスも十分にいい出来だったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But your singing and your dancing went so well yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "歌とダンスは確かに評判は良かったかもしれないけど\n……MCが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe people were pleased with my singing and dancing‚\nbut the talk segment…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "私の声が、聞こえにくかったって……\nそれで減点だって……書かれてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say that my voice was hard to hear…\nand that cost me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに声援が大きかったし聞こえ辛いところもあったな\nでも気にし過ぎなくていい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There was a lot of noise from the crowd which made it hard to hear sometimes‚\nbut you don’t need to worry about that so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、さくらちゃんのMCは\nはっきり聞こえたって、書いてある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But they say they could clearly hear\nSakura-chan when she talked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "それにアドリブのパートで、趣味の釣りのこと\n私に、話を振ってもらえたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And in the AdLib part‚ about my fishing hobby‚\nthey brought up the subject for me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "頭まっしろになって……\nでも……黙ってちゃ……ダメって思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but my mind went blank.\nI thought I couldn’t just stay silent‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "トークに、自信がないから、余計に……\n声が小さくなった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I have no confidence in talking‚\nso my voice went quiet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか……。でも、今はぎこちなくてもいい\nこれから場数を踏んで、少しずつうまくなっていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Well‚ no point feeling awkward about it now.\nAs you do more shows‚ you’ll get better gradually.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、声は、聞こえないと、ダメ……\nファンのみんなが、がっかりしてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ it’s not good if people can’t hear my voice…\nThe fans were disappointed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "MCも、ライブの大切な魅力の……ひとつだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The talk segment is one of the important attractions of a live show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、そうだけど、雫達はまだまだ新人だ\nこれからだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it is‚ Shizuku‚ but you’re still new at it.\nIt's just a start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんや、芽衣ちゃんは\n凄くうまい、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan and Mei-chan are\nreally good… at it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あの二人は、うまいっていうより話すのが好きだからな\n元々物怖じしない性格だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More than being good at it‚ those two just really love to talk.\nThey were just born with that bold personality…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんも、話すのは苦手だって言ってたけど……\n最近は、頑張って、ます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan said she has trouble speaking too‚\nbut she’s been trying harder lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "少なくとも、私みたいに、声が、ぼそぼそは\nしてない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At least she doesn’t\nmumble like I do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
