      "text": "私も、頑張って\n性格を改善しないと、です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to try harder too‚\nand improve my personality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんみたいに、「私の虜にしてあげますわ！」\nとか、言えるように、なる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll learn to say things like “I’ll captivate you‚”\nlike Suzu-chan does.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
