      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ。確かに声は聞こえた方がいいけど\n性格まで変える必要はないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute. It’s certainly better if people can hear your voice‚\nbut there’s no need to change your personality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "雫には雫の個性がある。それが魅力なんだ\nファンのみんなは今の雫が好きなんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have your own personality‚ Shizuku. That’s your appeal.\nThe fans like you as you are‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.7
    },
    {
